channel.title: Project 69
channel.description:
When i played project 69 before Rune-flare went off it was going through a crisis and i decided to play Project 69.
Btw this was 2 months ago
When i logged on i leveled for a bit and then a deal came across for me from an admin on there he said to donate rs accs for donator status i took this offer gave him my account on runescape a level 105 with 99 fletching i workred very hard on this and i got 3 phats on there and he said hell get eli the owner to make me donator i waited a week and stil lnothing apparently he was a scammer and eli deleted his acc.
i begged the owner eli for some compensation to my acc like donator status or items he said n oand said it was my own fault.
What was a supposed to believe when a admin on there said he was co-owner and i had an rs acc and he was taking them for donation of course i took this and im left with no acc and nothing so i quit and now im warning people project 69 are not friendly people.
Heed my warning...
